  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at First level of this class mod, you learn to use powerful techniques known as Kinetic Arts. These arts are quick and powerful. They are the manifestation of raw speed, and the hight of the Namikaze. You learn two arts of your choice; you learn more as you level up this class mod.</p><p>Kinetic art save DC = 12 + your level in this class mod + your proficiency bonus</p><p>Kinetic art attack bonus = Twice your proficiency bonus + your level in this class mod.</p><p>Beginning at 4th level of this class mod, whenever you cast a Kinetic art, your movement speed increases by 5 times the cost, until the end of your next turn. If you stack this effect, when you hit with a melee attack, you deal an extra 5d8 wind damage, as you unleash a burst of raw speed.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
